trans-unit.source: Keep original images:If set, uploaded images will never be overwritten by pngquant (i.e. only processed images will be converted)
Executable for pngquant:Full path for pngquant command
Quality:Don't save below min, use less colors below max (0-100)
Workaround for IE6:IE6 only displays fully opaque pixels. pngquant will make almost-opaque pixels fully opaque and will avoid creating new transparent colors.
